Package common.controllers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameChecker
    Provides necessary static methods to check if the game is over or should go to the next level.
    GameLevelBuilder
    This class builds all level worlds for the game and provides the interface for game designers to make changes on the game.
    IntersectionDitector  
    ObjectsGetter
    This class provides static method(s) to get all objects in one class in a given world.
    ScoreFileProcesser
    This class provides static methods to access to local score file and write to local score file.
    SpeedController
    This class provides static methods to get and set the speed of one class of objects in a world.
